{"tid":1496914,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［突發］香港已送中    五大訴求已經冇用！","createTime":"2019-08-22T17:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T18:18:36.000Z","uid":188828,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"828ed6454ea936493d99758b82f3cffaa33801ca","tid":1496914,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:22:39.000Z","msg":"呢排勇武活動冇之前咁密<br />\n但仍然有好多事發生緊...<br />\n冷靜落黎諗一諗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港好似一早係我地掛住吃喝玩樂既時候送咗中</span></span><br />\n唔知大家有冇同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n匯豐 國泰先後跪低<br />\n國泰有機師 空姐因為支持反送中活動就俾人抄<br />\n好早之前 有個老師係網上發表意見 又俾人清算<br />\n前排有讀law既學生因為發表反送中活動而被拒執業資格<br />\n香港警察無法無天 係警署入面打到人重傷 骨折 入院 （甚至可能有女義士受到凌辱）<br />\n同大陸公安有咩分別？<br />\n我地連手足既情況都唔知 好多可能出返黎已經身心靈受創 又被要脅家人而唔敢指證警察<br />\n就算指證 警方只係告傷人 好似醫院單野咁<br />\n仲未講已經一車車大陸公安混入香港<br />\n<br />\n其實現實就話我地知<br />\n五大訴求第一點<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">全面撒回送中條例已經係子烏虛有<br />\n因為我地已經被送中</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係好無力<br />\n有權執法既人用權力震壓<br />\n連事都可以俾佢地改寫成另一個故事<br />\n而仲有班冇腦既豬會信<br />\n我真係好撚嬲<br />\n<br />\n最近聽好多人講返大陸過關都出事<br />\n令我諗起<br />\n其實有冇諗過 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就算中共最後跪低俾我地有五大訴求<br />\n我地都係會成為階下囚？</span></span><br />\n你諗下 宜家呢個情況佢已經玩到捉人 禁錮人 派黑社會斬人<br />\n乜你覺得有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">五大訴求之後</span></span>佢會將所有野<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">一筆勾銷？</span></span><br />\n同你做<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">返一家人？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔會囉 </strong></span></span>佢一定會繼續清算<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉晒每一個抗爭者 暗地裡被自殺被失蹤</span></span><br />\n然後等香港抗爭者滅絕晒之後<br />\n再光明正大紅化香港<br />\n<br />\n我講咁多<br />\n係想提提大家<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有五大訴求都係唔安全<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n更可況政府想改風向想要我地有獨立調查就了事<br />\n唔撚得<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求係基本野<br />\n但基本野唔等於贏</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n認同既幫手推推<br />\n想多啲手足諗多少少<br />\n究竟我地想要乜野 點為之勝利？"},{"pid":"5cf868261441fc472a52d499585c3d82cb602aa0","tid":1496914,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:22:58.000Z","msg":"自推10下"},{"pid":"fa178f65b7fb85f1d1bc7779f4eecc47352d9d6b","tid":1496914,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:23:09.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"532731232e75213e6698a6e3d25e65823133fec0","tid":1496914,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:23:19.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"d87a276aa7f97a2f565bc1e57e1b4e6da19fb5cc","tid":1496914,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:23:29.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"097aa58fb7c760441a8a94879bdb2a3849d4e320","tid":1496914,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:23:43.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"5b9ca84d8ba29a3aa159f2933db69be882c2f9f5","tid":1496914,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:24:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24999cd26135b11184853140fcbfcccae3434827","tid":1496914,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:24:41.000Z","msg":"單腳企"},{"pid":"98df6e31a1ff0f7f04f45e163ca6a5f00658cd3f","tid":1496914,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:25:01.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"44ce894c6f95fc0b8190c81d1ca3f3e1816ca692","tid":1496914,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:2